    {
      "id": "dMdADGJNSYPLrmp7_Z6aC",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -142.84649964087316,
      "y": -702.4187421262081,
      "width": 1503.2695187029399,
      "height": 735,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aC",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2129807778,
      "version": 602,
      "versionNonce": 79534654,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1784224185880,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- Goal: >= 80% Automation, Satisfaction > 4.5/5, Response 95% < 2.5s\n- Scope: Generating, Scoring, Validation and Optimisation\n- Workflow:\n    - Client Input: \"I want to offer discount to tech professionals\" + CLIENT DATA\n    - Agent 1 (Generation): Creates offer → \"30% off Pro plan\"\n    - Agent 2 (Scoring): Rates offer → \"Score: 8/10\"\n    - Agent 3 (Validation): Checks if valid → \"Approved ✓\" --> Based on Rules (max discount 50%, ...)\n    - Agent 4 (Optimization): Improves it → \"Add urgency: 48hr deadline\"\n    - Show Result: Client sees final optimized offer\n- System Design:\n    - We have Centralized Orchestration.\n- Rules:\n    - Generate Marketing Offre Based on Client Data\n    - Score The Offre (0<=S<=100) and Predict churn \n    - Validate The Offre (Human Validation)\n    - Optimise The Offre (Suggest Optimisation on Some Parts)\n- Backend and Database\n    - Data Storage to Relation Database or Vector DB\n- Tips:\n    - skill.md\n    - Agent-to-Agent Communication",
      "fontSize": 28,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Goal: >= 80% Automation, Satisfaction > 4.5/5, Response 95% < 2.5s\n- Scope: Generating, Scoring, Validation and Optimisation\n- Workflow:\n    - Client Input: \"I want to offer discount to tech professionals\" + CLIENT DATA\n    - Agent 1 (Generation): Creates offer → \"30% off Pro plan\"\n    - Agent 2 (Scoring): Rates offer → \"Score: 8/10\"\n    - Agent 3 (Validation): Checks if valid → \"Approved ✓\" --> Based on Rules (max discount 50%, ...)\n    - Agent 4 (Optimization): Improves it → \"Add urgency: 48hr deadline\"\n    - Show Result: Client sees final optimized offer\n- System Design:\n    - We have Centralized Orchestration.\n- Rules:\n    - Generate Marketing Offre Based on Client Data\n    - Score The Offre (0<=S<=100) and Predict churn \n    - Validate The Offre (Human Validation)\n    - Optimise The Offre (Suggest Optimisation on Some Parts)\n- Backend and Database\n    - Data Storage to Relation Database or Vector DB\n- Tips:\n    - skill.md\n    - Agent-to-Agent Communication",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
